description: Sunlight filters in through the gazebo's slatted ceiling and creates a series of shadowed stripes upon the wooden floor.  A few birds hop about on the nearby grass, hoping for handouts.

Moonlight filters in through the gazebo's slatted ceiling and creates a series of soft shadowed stripes upon the wooden floor.  A cat has managed to climb on top of the gazebo's roof and is napping quietly up there.
title: [Courtyard, Gazebo]
